        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Maintain Diamond Purity",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Maintain Diamond Purity</h2><ul><li>Clean your diamonds regularly with warm water and mild soap.<br/></li><li>Use a soft brush to remove dust or oil.<br/></li><li>Store jewelry separately to prevent scratches.</li><li>Get professional cleaning annually.<br/></li></ul><p>For example, a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/diamond-tennis-braceletthe\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">diamond tennis bracelet</span></a> can maintain its shine for years with routine care and safe storage.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how-to-maintain",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_YRjUxp": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Maintain_Diamond_Purity_16_9_944f81c6-f0b1-494e-a59a-3d7cdbc8091c.png",
            "text": "<h2>When to Seek Professional Evaluation</h2><p>If your diamond appears cloudy or dull, or you’re unsure about its certification, visit a professional jeweler. Lucira offers virtual consultations and personalized advice to help you understand and verify your diamond’s purity with ease.When to Seek Professional Evaluation</p><p>If your diamond appears cloudy or dull, or you’re unsure about its certification, visit a professional jeweler. Lucira offers virtual consultations and personalized advice to help you understand and verify your diamond’s purity with ease.</p>",
