        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion – Choose Certified Purity with Lucira Jewelry</h2><p>Checking diamond purity doesn’t need to be complicated. From simple home tests to professional certifications, every step helps you make an informed choice. At Lucira Jewelry, every diamond natural or lab-grown is IGI-certified, ethically sourced, and crafted for lifelong brilliance.</p><p>Discover your perfect piece from Lucira’s exclusive collection of certified diamonds today.<br/> Shop now at <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a> and experience the purity you can trust.</p>",
